        <name xml:lang="en">heat, from steam, in chemical industry</name>
        <unitName xml:lang="en">MJ</unitName>
        <comment xml:lang="en">EcoSpold01Location=RER
Calculated based on literature data published by the GENDORF Chemical Park. The factory produced an average of 2462760 tonnes of chemical substances (including intermediates) per year in the years 2015-2019. The average consumption of steam (internal and external sources) in the years 2015-2019 was 511785800 MJ per year. This equals 0.2078 MJ/kg chemical produced.

